channel.description:
[center]Hi. My internet is going away in a few days and I'm trying to download everything I can. I thought this would be a perfect time to finally start and finish an rsps project.
Here's what I'm looking for:
[ul][li]A source/client that would be ideal for me to make my first project on.[/li] [li]Any downloadable files that would help me; being to study or what not.[/li][/ul]
Any help is appreciated! [/center]
